      "span_text": "In that range, household waste reduction effort has a constant marginal waste reduction of ρ units, regardless of the total amount of waste at the end of production.  With this assumption, partial derivatives in Eqs. (1) to  above are simplified to w 1 = 1 and w 2 = −ρ."
